longBusinessSummary: Indowind Energy Limited generates and distributes power through windmills in India. The company involved in setting up, operating, and maintaining wind farms. It also provides project and asset management; and value addition services, as well as trades in and sells carbon credits. It serves corporates and state utilities customers. Indowind Energy Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Chennai, India.
